    "description": "<p>We are a Food and Beverage company who has been around since 2007. We specialise in Vietnamese-inspired cuisine, Western cuisine, fast food, as well as local cuisines.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We operate and own a restaurant at the heart of Shenton Way as well as 4 cloud kitchens with Deliveroo and GrabFood (Tanjong Katong, Buona Vista, Aljunied and Hillview).&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are a small set up and we are always looking for like-minded individuals to join our team as we expand. You will be provided with training, food and other benefits if you join us. Individuals who would like to explore a career with us can also drop by our restaurant at 6A Shenton Way #02-28 Singapore 068815 to find out more.&nbsp;</p>",
